OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FIran has launched a wave of
OL,7,Fretaliatory attacks across the Middle
OL,8,FEast after US-Israeli strikes killed
OL,9,FSupreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei
OL,10,Fjust one day after conflict began.
OL,12,FIran and allied armed groups fired
OL,13,Fmissiles at Israel, Arab states and US
OL,14,Fmilitary targets around the region on
OL,15,FMonday, with previously safe havens
OL,16,Flike Dubai coming under fire, and
OL,17,Fhundreds of thousands of airline
OL,18,Fpassengers stranded around the globe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
