CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FAt least 555 people have been killed
OL,7,Fin strikes by Israel and US, while the
OL,8,FUS death toll stands at four.
OL,10,FThe Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps
OL,11,F(IRGC) vowed to deliver a "severe,
OL,12,Fdecisive and regret-inducing
OL,13,Fpunishment" after Khamenei's death.
OL,15,FITV News takes a look at what Iran's
OL,16,Fweapons arsenal looks like.
OL,18,FWhat weapons does Iran have?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FIran is home to one of the largest and
OL,7,Fmost diverse missile arsenals in the
OL,8,FMiddle East, defence analysts say.
OL,10,FThis includes mortars, rockets, drones
OL,11,Fand cruise missiles, which are
OL,12,Fdesigned to fly at low altitudes and
OL,13,Fstrike targets on the ground, Iran
OL,14,Fanalyst Behnam Ben Taleblu told ITV
OL,15,FNews.
OL,17,FThe "higher tier" of weaponry are the
OL,18,Fballistic missiles, which have a
OL,19,Fguided rocked-powered ascent but then
OL,20,Ffollow a freefall trajectory towards
OL,21,Ftheir target, he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,F"Ballistic missiles have only grown in
OL,7,Fimportance for the Islamic Republic,"
OL,8,FTaleblu said. "This is Iran's most
OL,9,Fimportant long-range strike tool."
OL,11,FBallistic missiles can be short-range,
OL,12,Fmedium-range and long-range. The
OL,13,Ffurthest of these could reach up to
OL,14,F3,000km, but Iran has a self-imposed
OL,15,Fcap of 2,000km.
OL,17,FIranian officials have stated 2,000km
OL,18,Fis enough to protect the country as it
OL,19,Fallows them to reach Israel, but
OL,20,FWestern analysts warn the limit could
OL,21,Fbe removed at any time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FIn 2023, Iranian state media unveiled
OL,7,Fpictures of hypersonic ballistic
OL,8,Fmissiles named Fattah-1 and Fattah-2,
OL,9,Fwhich the Islamic Revolutionary Guard
OL,10,FCorps claimed can reach up to 1,400km
OL,11,Fand travel 15 times the speed of sound.
OL,13,FThe regime has been striving to
OL,14,Fincrease its combat-readiness over the
OL,15,Flast two decades, and has improved the
OL,16,Frange, precision, mobility,
OL,17,Fsurvivability and lethality of
OL,18,Fballistic missiles, research has shown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FOne-way attack drones - also known as
OL,7,Fsuicide drones, due to their self-
OL,8,Fdestruction - have also extended
OL,9,FIran's long-range strike power at a
OL,10,Flower cost than missiles.
OL,12,FHow big is Iran's weapons arsenal?
OL,14,FThe exact number of Iran's missiles is
OL,15,Funclear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FIn 2022, US Central Command's General
OL,7,FKenneth McKenzie said Iran had more
OL,8,Fthan 3,000 ballistic missiles, but
OL,9,Fmany weapons were either used or
OL,10,Fdestroyed during the 12-day war last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FIsraeli officials claimed Iran's
OL,14,Fsupply of ballistic missile launchers
OL,15,Fwas cut in half during the war, but
OL,16,Fsatellite images have shown the regime
OL,17,Fhad largely rebuilt its programme
OL,18,Fsince June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FWeapons have also been moved
OL,7,Funderground, in a bid to protect them
OL,8,Ffrom strikes.
OL,10,F"There is no way of truly knowing what
OL,11,Fthe Iran regime has left," said Rosa
OL,12,FFreedman, a Professor of Law Conflict
OL,13,Fand Global Development at Reading
OL,14,FUniversity.
OL,16,F"But, as you can see from the last two
OL,17,Fdays, they were ready to go."
OL,19,FHow far can Iran's missiles reach?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FWith Iran's self-imposed cap, the
OL,7,Fregime's ballistic missiles can reach
OL,8,Fcountries in a radius of 2,000km
OL,9,Faround the country.
OL,11,FThis contains the entire Middle East
OL,12,Fregion, as well parts of Western
OL,13,FAfrica, Eastern and South Asia.
OL,15,FUS President Donald Trump has
OL,16,Frepeatedly claimed Iran has developed
OL,17,Fmissiles that "could soon reach the
OL,18,FAmerican homeland", but there is no
OL,19,Fevidence to suggest this is the case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FAn unclassified assessment by the
OL,7,FDefense Intelligence Agenct (DIA) in
OL,8,F2025 said Iran had the potential to
OL,9,Fdevelop a missile with a range greater
OL,10,Fthan 5,500km - "should Tehran decide
OL,11,Fto pursue the capability" - by 2035.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FHow does this compare to the US and
OL,19,FIsrael?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
