PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FDespite the improvements in ballistic
OL,7,Fmissiles, Iran's weaponry "pales in
OL,8,Fcomparison" to Israel or the US,
OL,9,FTaleblu told ITV News.
OL,11,FOn Sunday, the Israel Defense Forces
OL,12,F(IDF) said that it had dropped more
OL,13,Fthan 1,200 munitions across Iran
OL,14,Fduring the attacks that killed
OL,15,FKhamenei.
OL,17,FThe strikes also killed Khamenei's
OL,18,Ffamily, and the army's chief of staff
OL,19,FGeneral Abdol Rahim Mousavi and
OL,20,Fdefence minister General Aziz
OL,21,FNasirzadeh.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
