PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772539378
OL,3,CWhat weapons does Iran have and how
OL,4,Cfar can they reach?
OL,6,FThe US military said B-2 stealth
OL,7,Fbombers had struck Iran's ballistic
OL,8,Fmissile facilities with 2,000-pound
OL,9,Fbombs, and Trump claimed nine Iranian
OL,10,Fwarships had been destroyed.
OL,12,FBefore launching its first strike, the
OL,13,FUS had been building up what Trump
OL,14,Fcalled an "armada" of American
OL,15,Ffirepower in the region, with analysts
OL,16,Fat the International Institute for
OL,17,FStrategic Studies estimating it
OL,18,Fincludes 10% of available US airpower.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
